Source-MD5: 78459fd3b293a89de198c8b055f1e68c

SourceDirectory: araneida_%v

CompileScript: /usr/bin/true

InstallScript: <<
  mkdir -p %i/share/common-lisp/source/araneida
  cp -Rp * %i/share/common-lisp/source/araneida
  mkdir -p %i/share/common-lisp/systems
  ln -s %p/share/common-lisp/source/araneida/araneida.asd %i/share/common-lisp/systems/araneida.asd
<<

PostInstScript: %p/sbin/register-common-lisp-source araneida
PreRmScript: %p/sbin/unregister-common-lisp-source araneida

DocFiles: doc/* LICENCE LICENCE-diff NEWS Notes README TODO

